{"tid":1310374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非】知道大家好想即刻達成件事所以先屌鳩或放負，但入一入黎先啦","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:40.000Z","uid":271554,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dba5703099c263941895ce9b39a6f571874de7fb","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡單黎講，<br />\n1）麻煩各位兄弟姐妹請再一次理解我地所追求嘅「自由意志」<br />\n2）可以預計，但千萬不可「批死」任何事情<br />\n3）唔好急於一步到位<br />\n4）負面權威式嘅屌，對自己人係無幫助</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你有時間有興趣可以睇下我對每一項嘅意見：</strong><br />\n1）自由意志其實同我地所追求既民主自由有好大關係，亦正正係體現緊「兄弟爬山」「不讉責、不分化」嘅理念。我地必需要期望同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>幫助身邊嘅人去用下大家個腦</strong></span>，唔好認為企係雞蛋嗰邊就一定係用咗腦，兩件事黎。真正保持住獨立思考而決定做每一件事，忌人云亦云。<br />\n<br />\n2）我估都有人同我一樣諗法？<br />\n第一次 69 我打定輸數應該人都唔多，自己出到咪出囉叫做盡咗力，點知一百萬。<br />\n612，前一晚我都批定香港人邊會咁神心去做丫，次次都係三分鐘熱度同聽日要返工返學，二讀都無人理架啦，誰料凌晨發夢去金鐘時一車車黑衫人倒屎咁早就野餐⋯<br />\n616，香港人應該攰架喇，幾嬲柒娥都好大家都應該咁熱唔會想再上街，出到80萬我都覺得堅，點知多過69。<br />\n圍警總，圍黎做咩啫又唔攞唔到入面既裝備，一定會流血收場或者第二日俾啲和理非割蓆啦，喂，冇喎，有風波但無想像中咁差喎。<br />\n71，撞立會？撞黎做乜？佔？斷水斷電又做唔到啲咩無啦無啦⋯班和理非又撚話暴力啦⋯無啦無啦。點知原來有理由去衝(外圍收唔到資訊所以好多人唔理解而屌左先)，仲上埋頭條，多咗好多外國傳媒主動黎做採訪，坊間和理非亦唔多極端反對。<br />\n77，新地點又怕有人搞事，香港人咁怕事都唔會出掛，點知行埋去旺角。喺旺角，咁撚多警做乜唔撤？(原來俾人包抄)，結果黑警露左好多黑材料出黎。<br />\n光復屯門，警渣都幾多創意令嗰班中間派睇多啲唔同角度。<br />\n連儂牆，發展到全港，仲伸延埋長輩圖實體版，雖然好多廢佬去搞事又出PO要人，而我係唔同意死守的，但幅牆確實令好多唔上黎嘅人聚咗佢地自己區既氣，亦發展到連真藍絲都搞唔清，因為我望見佢地嘅回應都已經曲直難分。<br />\n真心，事情每一刻都變，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經唔可以用「做乜乜必定乜乜」去思考</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n３）一步到位：我幾想聽日港共即刻下台，班狗官全部返去大灣區食甲醛米飲屎水。但無可能咁快除非耶蘇而家落黎見晒我地。太急啦，我某程度上係好撚支持勇鬥，但係呢一刻大部分都只係諗住衝一啲保守嘢、絕大部份人都有包袱時，勇武急唔黎。<br />\n大家要戒一戒即食麵嘅效果，如果時機係啱，你係一叫就可以成村人出黎同你衝，可惜呢刻未係。<br />\n又，而家多左好多後生既參與政治事件係好事，但確實佢地(包括好多成年人、佬、嬋)好大部份都係啱啱開始關心下身邊時事，所謂民智剛開，何必求大家速成進步呢？難聽啲講，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">心身都真係要受過血淋淋既教訓先會學到嘢、做到嘢</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n4）我知道大家都好撚嬲好撚忟，但請不要忘記班時事新人真係新人，如果啲老屎忽一埋位就屌鳩你做嘢柒又話你做錯晒啲嘢，你作為新人，你會肯放開嗰心去跟佢嗎？無人鍾意俾人鬧、指責、批評，市面上亦唔多人可以做到用平常心去聆聽有內容嘅指罵。<br />\n大家幫幫手做多DD嘢丫喂，好撚嬲，但如果真係想說服一個人做你想做的事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不如先收埋忿怒或怨婦嘅情緒先？易入口好多</span></strong>。如果你都係改變唔到風向，就再更加做多啲去推自己相信嘅事，攰嘅咪先做咗自己能做既事先。咁大班人，又無一個具體精神領袖，一定係咁。<br />\n<br />\n若你不同意，又有好理據，我打開埋大髀俾你<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"7ec966b76e72f62072f0f86dd3039e81e73beb09","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"點解要屌人係因為想做好件事，係咪先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b65015463251e2c53e89243a17e99ce66fd8cc","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"要人幫手做你想做的事，就係要搵個有效嘅切入點先啱架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170ef8fb6c288cd0895a828989ae5c4376ec42a","tid":1310374,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"4671332b9a0942858cb42426e9d8f73f64fef363","tid":1310374,"uid":109358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8dd169a11b48f583143668654094ea0270e6618","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"其實D「正面宣傳手法」聽落去好鳩，但真係重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4579b74e745edc78004e60fa66c6f12aedfa7db9","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"過氣一哥為左重整軍心都會話「你地無做錯！」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa142d7d9f270c5ba4c8892577366cf0e20c0f8","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好死守幅牆，帶返好嗰風向就夠，無需屌嗰班用心去想做好件事既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd7c119fea2c3ac7cc356743323a556f8e5f267","tid":1310374,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"中國人係要屌，屌完就會折衷中和一下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cb9250516397b2ccaa97323e5a57093355c926","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd7c119fea2c3ac7cc356743323a556f8e5f267","tid":1310374,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"中國人係要屌，屌完就會折衷中和一下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"如果屌完對方肯用腦又唔係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過而家似係連登你自己內部屌，出去守嘅都係會守<br />\n如果硬唔得，不如軟咗先啦"},{"pid":"9ad4aded11574ad6030e9a0533a96a78bd36a37f","tid":1310374,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n<br />\n[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1af9cabd54e0f270fffd73f33e929f4913c2f6e4","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252e4c801e4ae3214ba8256493b1b3c0b74f990b","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4126feab12ae01dd58b606bb5c6b68b2be24fc6","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:29:35.000Z","msg":"根據經驗，每次活動都無先知係成功預測，不如就唔好再批死任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e43688b378bfc60f95b1c067475d290fe3581a1","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"大家要真係動動腦去分析資訊，公義唔會係人地話俾你聽就等於公義，公義係要你自己去思考過再做出黎先係"},{"pid":"3b06ab601ccd9f813ec530e77fbb899058060089","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:12:22.000Z","msg":"推返上黎先<br />\n經過尋日上水，多左好多內鬥聲音互屌<br />\n在現場嘅情緒激動，<br />\n去外圍嘅過份理性，<br />\n<br />\n大家都深白三五毛嘅存在<br />\n佢地係屌唔走，因為目標就係想你屌佢<br />\n也<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但我地自己友互屌無用啊</span><br />\n正面鼓勵係加乘力量<br />\n負面屌黎屌去只令大家都嬲，仲要有無形嘅框制肘住<br />\n</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好框住大家啊喂，而家要兩邊和勇都齊齊開花</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔係要阻止大家各自嘅情緒<br />\n只求間中溫馨提醒<br />\n相信自己，相信同路人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243ad428fd127a7a9d1f2fee748d9bef1ce81bbd","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"推返上黎先<br />\n經過尋日上水，多左好多內鬥聲音互屌<br />\n在現場嘅情緒激動，<br />\n去外圍嘅過份理性，<br />\n<br />\n大家都深白三五毛嘅存在<br />\n佢地係屌唔走，因為目標就係想你屌佢<br />\n也<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但我地自己友互屌無用啊</span><br />\n正面鼓勵係加乘力量<br />\n負面屌黎屌去只令大家都嬲，仲要有無形嘅框制肘住<br />\n</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好框住大家啊喂，而家要兩邊和勇都齊齊開花</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔係要阻止大家各自嘅情緒<br />\n只求間中溫馨提醒<br />\n相信自己，相信同路人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6315605ce884cd73bd548b2ba32916bbf4352fed","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"又出現了<br />\n推返上黎<br />\n<br />\n大家屌少陣啦，成長真係要時間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f06b65a9d57d80bbc194b32faeb9a05e23c0ee","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"又出現了<br />\n推返上黎<br />\n<br />\n大家屌少陣啦，成長真係要時間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46db6c59ad678cde7ca6065b7d18d3b4334992a","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"又出現了<br />\n推返上黎<br />\n<br />\n大家屌少陣啦，成長真係要時間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd16865e892912d1df64f672212a8a379386599","tid":1310374,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"又出現了<br />\n推返上黎<br />\n<br />\n大家屌少陣啦，成長真係要時間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}